      <title>世界银行向赞比亚提供 2 亿美元用于抗击干旱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-gives-zambia-200-million-for-drought-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据赞比亚财政部声明称，世界银行已批准向赞比亚再提供 2 亿美元赠款，帮助该国应对数十年来最严重的干旱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-gives-zambia-200-million-for-drought-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>估计法国左翼计划的成本将是马克龙计划的六倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新估算，参加法国立法议会选举的各政党做出的竞选承诺在成本上差异巨大，其中左翼联盟的承诺成本最高，主要是降低退休年龄的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债务互换后，瑞典央行被标普评为选择性违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/swedish-landlord-sbb-cut-to-selective-default-by-s-p</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的瑞典房地产公司 SBB 以大幅折扣启动将其债券兑换为新证券的交易，之后标普全球评级将 SBB 的评级下调至选择性违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/swedish-landlord-sbb-cut-to-selective-default-by-s-p</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞寻求多数席位，竞争对手联手阻止她</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日举行的法国立法选举最后一轮中，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟正在努力争取绝对多数，而竞争对手则在竭尽全力阻止极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
